1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Nisi Marija, dragi gledatelji, dobrodošli u novu epizodu Ad_Deum_Podcasta, s nama je danas jedan fratar možda jednog malo neobičajnog, neredovitog puta do redovništva i svećeništva, rodom iz Metkovića, a sada župni vikar u Imotskom,_Fraivo_Rastočić,_Fraivo_Hvala Nisi Marija i dobro nam došli.

2
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin An Daomir.

3
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Fraivo, kako ste, šta imao u Imotskom?

4
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] A dobro, evo, počele su pripreme u Koruzmi za muku, za taj jedinstveni događaj koji se događa u našem Imotskom, znači na cvjetnicu samu, bude u prezorenje, u prezorenje same muke gospodina našega Isusa Krista u kojem se udjeluje cijeli grad, pa evo, u tim svom pripremama, a što se tiče

5
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] dalje rada župe, sve je standardno, sve nema nekih posebnih, sad smo oko toga, sad smo oko muke.

6
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, evo, Fraivo, evo, vaš put do fratra i svećenika nije bio nekako, da ga nazovemo tako, uobičajen, nije ono išao od sjemeništa ili iza srednje škole, mi ste te situacije, to sam godina ušli u postulatur, ili tako, pa evo, kako je izgledao taj vaš put?

7
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] To svjedočanstvo je jedno svjedočanstvo onoga kome se želimo dokazati, što želimo.

8
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:54,719
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, na primjer, kada Isus zove prve svoje apostole, on u tom trenutku kaže učinit ću vas i oni ga slijede bez z da su rekli, idu za njim.

9
00:01:55,680 --> 00:02:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dok, ako se sjetimo neprispodobe bogatog mladića koji dotrči Isusu, njemu fali ono malo, fali mu prijeći iz religioznosti u vjeru.

10
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što se taj mladić vjerojatno dokazivao drugima, ima, kaže, bogati mladić, imaju bogatstvo, dokazivao se drugima i on je došao do Isusa jer je Isus bio influencer onoga vremena.

11
00:02:26,180 --> 00:02:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, moje svjedočanstvo je upravo na tome tragu dokazivanje ljudima ili dokazivanja bogu.

12
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:47,120
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, kroz moj život, kroz srednju školu, možda se je rađao taj poziv, vjerojatno je, i on se je gradio,

13
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] međutim, pošao sam tada, kroz srednju školu, pošao sam na utaknice Hajduka gledati.

14
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:12,060
[SPEAKER_00] U tom navijačkom svijetu je jednostavno bilo jedno dokazivanje drugima jer ako si htio napredovati u tom navijačkom svijetu,

15
00:03:12,060 --> 00:03:24,979
[SPEAKER_00] moro si se dokazivati drugim ljudima, moro si činiti neke stvari koje su bile slika i prilika toga društva u kojem si bio.

16
00:03:24,979 --> 00:03:41,120
[SPEAKER_00] Da se još malo vratim nazad, imao sam dobar prosjek u osmom razredu, no međutim, ekipa me je povukla u srednju obrtničku školu.

17
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:50,560
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne omlažavam sada ništa. Ovo je važna priča kome se dokazivati, znači, da li se dokazivati ekipi ili se dokazivati Bogu.

18
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz taj navijački svijet sam se naučio puno toga.

19
00:03:54,800 --> 00:04:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je što smo naučili, to je jedno zajedništvo, kada pripadaš nečemu, taj osjećaj pripadnosti.

20
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:10,979
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to bi možda bila prva pouka današnjega ovoga moga gostovanja ovdje u vašem podcastu.

21
00:04:10,979 --> 00:04:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pouka pripadnjauta zajedništvu.

22
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:27,040
[SPEAKER_00] I to mislim da su mlađe generacije danas upravo po tom pripadanju zajednici, malo su, amo reći, pod navodne znake odrezane od toga.

23
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaju taj osjećaj pripadno zajednici. To je me naučio navijački svijet.

24
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:37,600
[SPEAKER_00] I druga stvar je povjerenje u drugu osobu. To je krivo.

25
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je skroz krivo. Znači, imaš povjerenje u čovjeka.

26
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaš u Boga, nego u čovjek.

27
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, kad te osoba ne iznevjeri, to jedno povjerenje gradi upravo naš odnos između dvije osobe.

28
00:04:54,420 --> 00:05:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] Taj razgovor oči u oči, taj susret sa drugom osobom, koje imamo zajednički cilj i nekako zajedničko druženje.

29
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] No, međutim, sve je to bilo dokazivanje drugim ljudima.

30
00:05:09,139 --> 00:05:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] Dokazivanje unutar same navijačke skupine, dokazivanje vanka, izlazaka, dokazivanje nečega što u stvari mi kao ljudi nismo.

31
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:31,660
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom dokazivanju se izgubi ovaj susret oči i u oči.

32
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:35,399
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što stalno bježiš od toga susreta.

33
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] Bježiš od susreta sa pojedincem.

34
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:41,259
[SPEAKER_00] Bježiš od susreta sa Bogom.

35
00:05:41,259 --> 00:05:44,459
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Zato što ti ovo čini trenutnu ugodu.

36
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,379
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo dobro vrijeme. Ja se ne stidim toga.

37
00:05:48,379 --> 00:05:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne stidim se nimalo toga vremena.

38
00:05:50,819 --> 00:05:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je bilo moje vrijeme u kojem sam ja sazrijevao i u vjeri i u odnosima sa ljudima.

39
00:05:58,220 --> 00:06:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] U kojem sam sazrijevao upravo u tome zajedništu i povjerenju jednih prema drugima.

40
00:06:06,139 --> 00:06:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije srednje škole dolazi jedno vrijeme bavljenja politikom u Metkoviću.

41
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ustaj na vijački živ.

42
00:06:18,819 --> 00:06:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je opet to jedno dokazivanje drugome.

43
00:06:23,019 --> 00:06:31,879
[SPEAKER_00] Znači dokazivanje da želiš neku ambiciju pretvoriti u konkretnu akciju.

44
00:06:32,259 --> 00:06:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet svoju ambiciju, opet bez Boga, bez...

45
00:06:35,699 --> 00:06:37,259
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jako traženje vlasti tog ja.

46
00:06:37,259 --> 00:06:39,660
[SPEAKER_00] Traženje vlasti tog ja i pumpanje ega.

47
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:41,120
[SPEAKER_00] Pumpanje ega.

48
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:45,459
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se događaju i prvi susreti sa društvenim mrežama.

49
00:06:45,459 --> 00:06:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] Vi mlađe generacije ne znate kada je to došao Facebook, to je bilo ono bum.

50
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] Komputer je bio, znači komputer je bio ekran ovliki, duboko ovliko kutija, ono...

51
00:06:57,079 --> 00:07:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kutija koda je danas spremljeno, ne znam, stolu u Ikeje u njoj.

52
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tolika je bila kutija za komputer.

53
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ti prvi susreti sa internetom, prvi susreti s nekim virtualnim svijetom i tu počinje pomalo pumpanje svoga ja, svoga ega.

54
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:21,620
[SPEAKER_00] Svojega onoga što je u tebi najgore.

55
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:25,600
[SPEAKER_00] I opet nema toga susreta oči u oči.

56
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] I opet nema dokazivanja Bogu, nego da opet je to dokazivanje nekim drugim ljudima, nekim drugim stvarima, nekim drugim ideološkim postavkama.

57
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,879
[SPEAKER_00] I jednostavno to te ne izgrađuje.

58
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:54,279
[SPEAKER_00] I događa se dakle 27. godina moga života, gdje sam ja prošao i ljubav i sa curama i gdje sam prošao.

59
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:56,879
[SPEAKER_00] Prolazi joj život kao ja mladi čovjek, jel?

60
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi 27. godina i dolazi jedan politički sastanak u Zagrebu.

61
00:08:04,699 --> 00:08:12,819
[SPEAKER_00] I gore bi ja bila jedna mlada cura.

62
00:08:12,819 --> 00:08:17,459
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ću ja nešto kasanje, ono dokazivanje.

63
00:08:17,459 --> 00:08:25,439
[SPEAKER_00] Opet to napumpano moje, ja napumpano to, napumpano to, ja sam u stranci, ja sam ovo, ja sam ono.

64
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ipak mene sad, tad već te prate, prate te većina ljudi, tada je bilo oko 3-4 tisće pratitelja, to je za danas veliko, a kam al tada.

65
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] 3-4 tisće pratitelja na Facebooku, sa sestrom Marijom Pijom sam počeo pisati blog, kristocentric.

66
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom, ono, dovedeš sebe u tu situaciju, ono, da si ti nešto.

67
00:08:54,740 --> 00:09:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] U to se pokreću i neke kolumne, neke stranice se otvaraju.

68
00:09:00,059 --> 00:09:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] I eto, stolikog ega, evo samo da vam objasnim koliki je to ego bio.

69
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:18,720
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u tom trenutku, kad bi se ja upoznava s osobom koja je u crkvi, koja je katolik, koja je tu negdje i političkog opredeljenja,

70
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] koja, ja bi ono rekao, ja sam imo Rastočići.

71
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] I sad bi se ja začudi, a kako ona mene ne zna smreža, znaš, svako bi ono rekao, ko si ti, znaš.

72
00:09:29,019 --> 00:09:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] Začudiš se, kako ti, ne znaš, popularnog blogera, popularnog sa Facebooka, znaš, ono, tu se borim protiv određenih manipulacija, kako mene ne znaš.

73
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,919
[SPEAKER_00] To je taj ego.

74
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, dok on dovede čovjeka, on dovede čovjeka da, ono, na ulici doslovno staneš i ono, kako me ne znaš, kako me ne možeš prepoznati.

75
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje dogodio se taj politički sastanak, dogodila se ta cura u Zagrebu i ona je rekla,

76
00:09:59,019 --> 00:10:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom trenutku da želi ići u Palmotićevu, bila je misa na večer, bilo je oko Svjetog Frane, to je dvoje jako onaj, jako simbolično, u kršćanskom smislu,

77
00:10:14,659 --> 00:10:22,700
[SPEAKER_00] da ide u Palmotićevu Baziliku srca Isusova na misu, na grobu Ivona Mirca.

78
00:10:23,659 --> 00:10:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nise ja tad, meni je tad bilo, ono, ja sam sa njoj nošao na tu misu, eto, dineš otići, razumiješ, di ćeš je ostaviti sam, diš ti je ostao u stanu, naš, otići, otići,

79
00:10:34,659 --> 00:10:35,580
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto radi reda.

80
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] E, baš ono, otići, doslovno sad kad vidi, no ovako odmaka, ono ruga sa se, da, nije nešto. Ja sam ošao tamo i ona je rekla da se ide ispoviditi u Bazilici.

81
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja ne znam ništa, Zagreb, ono, ja sam bila u Zagreba, nisam ja obilazio crkve.

82
00:10:57,139 --> 00:10:58,320
[SPEAKER_00] Viste bila u Maksimir.

83
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] E, nisam obilazio crkve, nego u Borogaj Maksimir, ono, znao se uvodite, policija provede do stadiona i to i to.

84
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] I, ona kaže tamo da se ide ispoviditi, aj, ja sam se išao ispoviditi, možda je to u meni bilo u podsvijesti, ja to prepisujem Duhu Svijetu.

85
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] I, meni je palo na pamet taj grob Ivana Merca. Ja sam pito ispovjednika, koji je tada ispovjedao, gdje je grob Ivana Merca.

86
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] I, on je meni pokazao, bija blizu te ispovjedaonce, u Bazilici srca Isusova.

87
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tamo kleknio i molio. Ja nisam bio svjestan toga.

88
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zamisli ona i sto četreskila čovičina velika kleči i moli.

89
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] A ja uopće ne beren. Sad ne možeš onaj zabuljeti kolno.

90
00:11:49,059 --> 00:11:53,299
[SPEAKER_00] I, uopće ne beren da sam ja tu molija.

91
00:11:53,299 --> 00:11:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je kasnije rekla ta cura, a vidi ćeš kako se to cijela priča razvila.

92
00:11:58,019 --> 00:12:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] I jednostavno, tu sam molija ispovj groba i ja sam samo digao, pričestija se i vratija se moli.

93
00:12:05,299 --> 00:12:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo se vraćali u taj stan.

94
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,419
[SPEAKER_00] Ko da se ništa nije dogodilo.

95
00:12:10,419 --> 00:12:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kupija sam sebi bocu Jack Danielsa, idemo mi sa u stan, idemo pit.

96
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:17,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ko da se ništa ovo nije prethodno dogodilo.

97
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] Došao sam u stan i u jednom trenutku vidio sam križ u tome stanu.

98
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,620
[SPEAKER_00] I to je sve bilo u kratko vremena.

99
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ta cura je počela kuhati večeru.

100
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se oša istušira.

101
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam izišao iz tuša, vidim taj križ.

102
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,120
[SPEAKER_00] I ja znam da sam tamo molija zdravu Mariju.

103
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] Pokpija rusak i oša ća.

104
00:12:55,179 --> 00:12:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa da sam javio.

105
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa da sam pokpija rusak i oša ća.

106
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ostade Jack, ostade sve tamo.

107
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nema, sve ono, propade.

108
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] Na, sve propade u tom trenutku.

109
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] I ja dolazim na autobusni kolodvor,

110
00:13:09,659 --> 00:13:11,379
[SPEAKER_00] kako sam ja imao prijevoza gore.

111
00:13:11,379 --> 00:13:13,580
[SPEAKER_00] Prijevoza gore, dogovoren.

112
00:13:13,580 --> 00:13:16,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ja dolazim na autobusni kolodvor

113
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] i tada sam imao točno 172 kune

114
00:13:20,179 --> 00:13:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] kako mi košta karta za autobus u Metkovići.

115
00:13:22,899 --> 00:13:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja još ne znam šta se dogodilo,

116
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] di se dogodilo.

117
00:13:28,139 --> 00:13:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam otišao,

118
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:32,240
[SPEAKER_00] uzeo rusak i oša doma.

119
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dajem otkaz u firmi,

120
00:13:34,159 --> 00:13:37,080
[SPEAKER_00] u jednoj firmi gdje sam radio,

121
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,919
[SPEAKER_00] dajem otkaz.

122
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] E sad ovo iduća radnja

123
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] se događa negdje u razmaku

124
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] šest, sedam mjeseci.

125
00:13:46,419 --> 00:13:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ne govorim ono,

126
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] tad je i tad bilo.

127
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom, dajem otkaz u firmi,

128
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] počinje nić,

129
00:13:55,259 --> 00:13:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] počinje nić na sve te emise redovito.

130
00:13:57,840 --> 00:14:03,279
[SPEAKER_00] Odjednom se neki molitvenici tu pojavljuju,

131
00:14:03,279 --> 00:14:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] kraj mene.

132
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazim u dodir sa Jozefo Ratzigerom

133
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,299
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovim knjigama.

134
00:14:08,299 --> 00:14:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] Preko jedne jako drage meni osobe

135
00:14:13,179 --> 00:14:14,100
[SPEAKER_00] i važne u životu,

136
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je Tomislav Medak iz Metkovića,

137
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] vjeru učitelj.

138
00:14:16,679 --> 00:14:19,799
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazim u dodir,

139
00:14:19,799 --> 00:14:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] znači sa Ratzingerom

140
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:23,399
[SPEAKER_00] i sad se mijenja sve.

141
00:14:23,399 --> 00:14:25,200
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste se vi u tom periodu

142
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] nekom povjeravali o tim promjenama ili nešto?

143
00:14:27,899 --> 00:14:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] Što nisam, ja nizam za njih.

144
00:14:29,299 --> 00:14:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] Nemoš ti iskušiti.

145
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:32,879
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko je taj ego moj bio da,

146
00:14:32,879 --> 00:14:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

147
00:14:34,179 --> 00:14:40,259
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno bi se ja i povjerio da nisam bio u tom nekom svijetu

148
00:14:40,259 --> 00:14:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ti nisi baš imao povjerenje u te ljude.

149
00:14:44,059 --> 00:14:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] O tim stvarima prič,

150
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer znaš kako ti ide?

151
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] Malo umisto,

152
00:14:49,559 --> 00:14:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] svi te znaju

153
00:14:51,179 --> 00:14:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] i neke priče dolaze već do tebe,

154
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,019
[SPEAKER_00] enoga poludio,

155
00:14:55,019 --> 00:14:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] enoga ovo.

156
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] I sad se ti malo i bojiš.

157
00:14:57,139 --> 00:14:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da, teško je reći.

158
00:14:58,460 --> 00:14:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo kome reći.

159
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] A i s druge strane,

160
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,080
[SPEAKER_00] ti ne znaš šta ti je bilo.

161
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam dotad bio ono,

162
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] vjernik,

163
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] tradicijski,

164
00:15:07,659 --> 00:15:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

165
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:09,120
[SPEAKER_00] gdje neće,

166
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] inače,

167
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] naš obiteljski nadmak je tica.

168
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,120
[SPEAKER_00] Obiteljski,

169
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] gdje neće mali tica biti na veliki petak u procesi,

170
00:15:17,179 --> 00:15:19,240
[SPEAKER_00] gdje neće biti na veliku subotu,

171
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

172
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] na uskrz,

173
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:21,419
[SPEAKER_00] na božić.

174
00:15:21,419 --> 00:15:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto da se vidite.

175
00:15:22,299 --> 00:15:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] E, e, e.

176
00:15:23,220 --> 00:15:25,879
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje neće on biti u procesi i tako.

177
00:15:25,879 --> 00:15:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] I,

178
00:15:28,299 --> 00:15:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] ta se promjena vidila na meni,

179
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja nisam mogao prepoznati.

180
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znaš,

181
00:15:34,679 --> 00:15:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaš šta je,

182
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno ne znaš.

183
00:15:36,059 --> 00:15:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] Par puta sam išao pješke u Međugorje,

184
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] a to je ništa,

185
00:15:40,279 --> 00:15:41,279
[SPEAKER_00] Metković, Međugorje,

186
00:15:41,279 --> 00:15:41,919
[SPEAKER_00] to je malo.

187
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:44,419
[SPEAKER_00] I jednom sam išao pješke u Sinj,

188
00:15:44,419 --> 00:15:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] a ovo je važna tu poveznica.

189
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:50,100
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam došao u Sinj,

190
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:52,100
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo na veliku gospu.

191
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] Fra Antonijom Rava,

192
00:15:56,139 --> 00:15:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] koji je i sad u Sinju.

193
00:15:58,139 --> 00:16:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] mi je dao životopis,

194
00:16:00,519 --> 00:16:01,379
[SPEAKER_00] onaj,

195
00:16:01,379 --> 00:16:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] dao mi životopis Svjetoga Frane,

196
00:16:03,299 --> 00:16:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] ili neki Moltvenik,

197
00:16:04,279 --> 00:16:05,899
[SPEAKER_00] sad ne mogu točno onaj.

198
00:16:05,899 --> 00:16:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer jedan Moltvenik mi je,

199
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,799
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne,

200
00:16:08,799 --> 00:16:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je dao Moltvenik,

201
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] a Paško Slovenac,

202
00:16:11,659 --> 00:16:12,899
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam li on više živ,

203
00:16:12,899 --> 00:16:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] što je ispovjedao u Međugorju,

204
00:16:14,860 --> 00:16:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] on ovako nizak,

205
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] mal Slovenac,

206
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:19,080
[SPEAKER_00] stano je bio u Međugorju.

207
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ne znam li živ,

208
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] tada je bio jako staristo.

209
00:16:22,419 --> 00:16:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] onaj,

210
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:24,759
[SPEAKER_00] znam da je bio Slovenac,

211
00:16:24,759 --> 00:16:25,980
[SPEAKER_00] i Paško da se zvao,

212
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:28,120
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je dao životopis Svjetoga Frane.

213
00:16:28,799 --> 00:16:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] I ja nisam mogao taj životopis

214
00:16:31,559 --> 00:16:33,919
[SPEAKER_00] pročita dalje od onoga obraćenja.

215
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:34,919
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je bilo baza,

216
00:16:34,919 --> 00:16:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] kako je ono bi ja berekin,

217
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] kako je ono,

218
00:16:36,519 --> 00:16:38,879
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno sam se ja sotim indeficirao,

219
00:16:38,879 --> 00:16:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] sotim sam se,

220
00:16:40,179 --> 00:16:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] sotim sam se onaj,

221
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] našao sam se u tome,

222
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] nisam ga mogao dalje pročitati.

223
00:16:46,059 --> 00:16:47,299
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se dogodilo,

224
00:16:47,299 --> 00:16:48,580
[SPEAKER_00] taj referendum,

225
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] referendum za brak,

226
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] se dogodio,

227
00:16:52,159 --> 00:16:55,379
[SPEAKER_00] i onda su mene neki ljudi zvali,

228
00:16:55,379 --> 00:16:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] bili ja bio koordinator,

229
00:16:56,679 --> 00:16:59,399
[SPEAKER_00] jer iz toga sam iziša,

230
00:16:59,399 --> 00:17:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] ehe, ehe, ehe,

231
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] i onaj,

232
00:17:02,519 --> 00:17:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam tada rekao,

233
00:17:03,899 --> 00:17:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] šta se men dogodilo u Zagrebu,

234
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,720
[SPEAKER_00] šta se men dogodilo to,

235
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] tim ljudima, svećenicima,

236
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] i onda su on rekli,

237
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] to mogao bi poziviti,

238
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] to je men prvi susret,

239
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] uopće da bi to mogao bi poziviti,

240
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] za svećenika, jel?

241
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] I u to,

242
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] u to vrijeme zove ta iz Zagreba,

243
00:17:22,099 --> 00:17:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] ta cura.

244
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] I govori ona meni,

245
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] kao,

246
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam jako žalosna,

247
00:17:28,759 --> 00:17:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] šta si ti oša,

248
00:17:29,859 --> 00:17:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] bla, bla, bla,

249
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] da je ona razbijala,

250
00:17:32,539 --> 00:17:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] gore, posudje,

251
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] ko će to nju platiti,

252
00:17:35,079 --> 00:17:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] ja govorim,

253
00:17:36,019 --> 00:17:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] ti još luđa odavi,

254
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovo mi govore da idem u popet,

255
00:17:38,579 --> 00:17:40,660
[SPEAKER_00] i mi govoriš da si razbijala posudje,

256
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

257
00:17:40,980 --> 00:17:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] šta je ovo,

258
00:17:42,259 --> 00:17:43,299
[SPEAKER_00] šta se događa?

259
00:17:43,299 --> 00:17:45,160
[SPEAKER_00] I ona meni kaže tada,

260
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] stani, stani malo,

261
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

262
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] naš ti da si ti tu veče prekleća,

263
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] kraj groba imena mjerica.

264
00:17:52,359 --> 00:17:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

265
00:17:52,559 --> 00:17:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je posla,

266
00:17:53,319 --> 00:17:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] nema šta,

267
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] e tad je meni,

268
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] ta se ja prvi,

269
00:17:57,619 --> 00:17:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] moj prvi dodir,

270
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] to je nakon 7-8 meseci od Palmotića,

271
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] je moj prvi dodir,

272
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] moj prvi dodir sa,

273
00:18:04,319 --> 00:18:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] sa pozivom.

274
00:18:06,519 --> 00:18:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] I dobro,

275
00:18:07,019 --> 00:18:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] i taj životop sveta Frane iz Međugorija,

276
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] taj sustret sa Frantonijom Ravkon,

277
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji je propovijedao nešto,

278
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] nešto o svetom Frani,

279
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:18,720
[SPEAKER_00] fratri koji su bili dole pokojni fra Petar Gulić,

280
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] fra Lukca Vojković i fra Kristijan Perković,

281
00:18:23,019 --> 00:18:25,480
[SPEAKER_00] bili u Metkoviću tada na župi,

282
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji su me prihvatili,

283
00:18:27,559 --> 00:18:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] možeš misli kakve su dolazle do njih priče u mene.

284
00:18:30,559 --> 00:18:30,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

285
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] E, ali oni su me stvarno otvore na srca prihvatili.

286
00:18:35,519 --> 00:18:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] I sad se tu sve to nekako počelo,

287
00:18:38,359 --> 00:18:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] taj mozaik poziva se počeo slagati,

288
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] počeo se slagati u jednu jasnu sliku,

289
00:18:46,559 --> 00:18:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

290
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:54,819
[SPEAKER_00] Jasnu sliku gdje se odjednom počneš dokazivati Bogu.

291
00:18:54,819 --> 00:18:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je bio taj klik,

292
00:18:57,819 --> 00:18:59,299
[SPEAKER_00] ja ti ne mogu reći.

293
00:18:59,299 --> 00:19:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu jedno sa onom.

294
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ne postoji taj točan trenut.

295
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoji taj točan,

296
00:19:04,519 --> 00:19:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] znači to je bio razvoj.

297
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ja možda mogu teško shvatiti,

298
00:19:09,059 --> 00:19:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja prihvatim,

299
00:19:10,039 --> 00:19:12,680
[SPEAKER_00] teško shvatiti ova blitz krik obraćenja naša.

300
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] tup tup odmah sutra.

301
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu.

302
00:19:15,539 --> 00:19:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mene je to ubija cijeli proces,

303
00:19:17,500 --> 00:19:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

304
00:19:17,779 --> 00:19:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dok sam jedan spodio.

305
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] Možda zato što sam jedan bio u tom krugu

306
00:19:21,799 --> 00:19:22,839
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam se,

307
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] nisi baš imao povjerenja u ljude,

308
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se uvijek nešto vagalo,

309
00:19:27,359 --> 00:19:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] neke igrice se igrale,

310
00:19:28,819 --> 00:19:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] neke igrice se igrale u krugu politike,

311
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] a možda vamo gdje si imao puno povjerenja u ljude

312
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] u tom navijačkom svijetu,

313
00:19:37,319 --> 00:19:40,200
[SPEAKER_00] gdje si imao jedno zajedništvo,

314
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali koje je bilo usmjereno na totalno nešto drugo,

315
00:19:42,779 --> 00:19:45,160
[SPEAKER_00] na nogometni klub,

316
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji ti je odveo skroz na drugu stranu.

317
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

318
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam to spoznao sam poziv,

319
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] u tim trenucima se dogodio taj klik.

320
00:19:56,660 --> 00:19:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] Iću ja u fratri.

321
00:19:59,180 --> 00:20:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] A kako baš fratri?

322
00:20:01,059 --> 00:20:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Jer su bili u Metkoviću, nemaš.

323
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

324
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, u nas ode u Hercegovini

325
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] i dole, dole, u Neretvi,

326
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] u Imotskom,

327
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,839
[SPEAKER_00] fratare, sve.

328
00:20:10,839 --> 00:20:11,339
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

329
00:20:11,339 --> 00:20:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] E, jedno samo to se dogodi.

330
00:20:13,559 --> 00:20:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] A i taj životop svijeta u frane

331
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:17,700
[SPEAKER_00] sam ti na Veliku Gospu u Sinju

332
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] pročita do kraja.

333
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] To sam ti ja reći malo prije.

334
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pročita do kraja.

335
00:20:22,119 --> 00:20:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] I svidija mi se taj frano,

336
00:20:24,019 --> 00:20:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] jako je dobar on čovjek bio.

337
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar je i danas.

338
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] Frano je dobar.

339
00:20:29,579 --> 00:20:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] I jednostavno sam se našao tu.

340
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem ti, primili su me ljudi,

341
00:20:34,519 --> 00:20:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] otvorili su mi župnu kuću

342
00:20:36,519 --> 00:20:40,700
[SPEAKER_00] krenija sam na taj put

343
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] fratarluka upravo priko toga.

344
00:20:44,339 --> 00:20:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

345
00:20:45,619 --> 00:20:47,680
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome svemu

346
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:49,740
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam imao najveće povjerenje

347
00:20:49,740 --> 00:20:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] i kom je bio najveći motor.

348
00:20:51,519 --> 00:20:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] Osim fratara.

349
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] ta osoba što sam spomenio, Tomislav Medak,

350
00:20:57,619 --> 00:20:58,259
[SPEAKER_00] on je bio.

351
00:20:58,259 --> 00:21:03,660
[SPEAKER_00] I druge, gdje sam najbolje primljen,

352
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] ali to su krive pobude.

353
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] Krive su pobude.

354
00:21:07,059 --> 00:21:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je u tom navijačkom svijetu.

355
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] zašto?

356
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

357
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer jednom ka si njihov,

358
00:21:13,799 --> 00:21:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] ti si njihov šta god napraviš u životu.

359
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] I tu sam primljen stvarno bez omalovažavanja,

360
00:21:22,819 --> 00:21:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] bez ono ismijavanja,

361
00:21:24,779 --> 00:21:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] bez ičega.

362
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] To jesu krive pobude.

363
00:21:27,579 --> 00:21:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] Da, malo čudno opet za pomisliti.

364
00:21:29,859 --> 00:21:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] Je, ali kad si jedno o njihov,

365
00:21:31,599 --> 00:21:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad si jedno o njihov,

366
00:21:32,460 --> 00:21:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] e tu se iskazuje to zajedništo i povjerenje.

367
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se upravo iskažuje.

368
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda danas mene zovnu neki za ispovijed,

369
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je i tu obraćenja,

370
00:21:41,559 --> 00:21:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je i tu obraćenja,

371
00:21:43,539 --> 00:21:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] zovnu me za ispovijed,

372
00:21:44,579 --> 00:21:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] zovnu me za razgovor,

373
00:21:45,859 --> 00:21:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] zovnu me kada kar ste dijete ili nešto,

374
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] ili se vinčaju u crkvi.

375
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] I okej.

376
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:55,299
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem ti, najbolje sam primljen u tome svijetu.

377
00:21:55,299 --> 00:21:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] I fratri, jel?

378
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:01,160
[SPEAKER_00] Fratri, baš primje fratara.

379
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] Fratarluk, da.

380
00:22:02,839 --> 00:22:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad se ušlo,

381
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] uđeš u taj žrvanj,

382
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:08,740
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam došao godinu dana u Imocki,

383
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] u poslaturu.

384
00:22:10,079 --> 00:22:15,859
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, opet tu se otvaraju neka druga pitanja,

385
00:22:15,859 --> 00:22:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja se inače,

386
00:22:16,579 --> 00:22:18,339
[SPEAKER_00] ako znate željna osoba dosta,

387
00:22:18,339 --> 00:22:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] ošti to uspit, nećeš uspit,

388
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] ćeš osramoti kuću.

389
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,299
[SPEAKER_00] I to ti ostaje negdje,

390
00:22:25,299 --> 00:22:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] to ti ostaje negdje.

391
00:22:28,539 --> 00:22:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] od roditelja sam bio

392
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:32,640
[SPEAKER_00] primljen,

393
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,740
[SPEAKER_00] majka je prosvetna djelatnica bila,

394
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] ona je to okej primila.

395
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] Čaču smo dobili pre gotov čin,

396
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] on je malo onako staromodano stanaš,

397
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] staromodano dišti u pope, dišti.

398
00:22:44,819 --> 00:22:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] A je bilo malo to čudno već,

399
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:48,160
[SPEAKER_01] ono, s 28 godina.

400
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, kako ne, kako ne,

401
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo čač i ajme.

402
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:53,839
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo ga ja i majka u dogovoru,

403
00:22:53,839 --> 00:22:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] u dogovoru, viš kog ti majka valja,

404
00:22:55,539 --> 00:22:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] u dogovoru smo ga doveli

405
00:22:57,380 --> 00:22:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] pred gotov čin,

406
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] pred samo,

407
00:23:00,039 --> 00:23:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] samo završetak.

408
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, ide je ni gotovo,

409
00:23:04,039 --> 00:23:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] nema tu priče.

410
00:23:05,359 --> 00:23:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, on ti je malo ono,

411
00:23:08,059 --> 00:23:08,740
[SPEAKER_00] kako bih rekao,

412
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:09,839
[SPEAKER_00] taj stariji čovjek ima.

413
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] Standardni on je naši ljudi stariji.

414
00:23:11,539 --> 00:23:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] Standardni je naši ljudi stariji.

415
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] I dogodi se taj imocki,

416
00:23:17,980 --> 00:23:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] znači, odjednom se nađeš

417
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:21,140
[SPEAKER_00] u tom jednom drugom svijetu,

418
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] drugom svijetu gdje nema više tih prijatelja,

419
00:23:24,839 --> 00:23:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] nema više lažnog prijateljstva.

420
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dokazivaš se Bogu,

421
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] e, sad dolazimo do toga obrata.

422
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] U tom trenutku,

423
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] kad se ja počinjem dokaziva Bogu,

424
00:23:34,299 --> 00:23:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad shvatim da je to poziv,

425
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi fratri daju svoje svjedočanstvo,

426
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] kad me prijatelji prihvate,

427
00:23:42,740 --> 00:23:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] i onda se počinje dokaziva Bogu.

428
00:23:46,559 --> 00:23:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tek vidiš

429
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to tvoje i ja

430
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] zatvaralo put prema Bogu.

431
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo ništa ja ne bi mogao svjedočiti,

432
00:23:55,279 --> 00:23:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] da se tada nisam otvorio Bogu

433
00:23:57,839 --> 00:23:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] i dijelovanju duha svijetog.

434
00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono učinit ću vas.

435
00:24:02,359 --> 00:24:04,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ne onaj bogati mladić

436
00:24:04,160 --> 00:24:06,299
[SPEAKER_00] koji ode tužan,

437
00:24:06,299 --> 00:24:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] zato što nije napravio

438
00:24:08,099 --> 00:24:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] taj korak naprijed prema vjeri.

439
00:24:11,380 --> 00:24:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] Nego ribar, neuk,

440
00:24:14,099 --> 00:24:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] dođeš neuku vjeri,

441
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] neuku fratrima,

442
00:24:18,099 --> 00:24:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] neuku svećenicima

443
00:24:19,359 --> 00:24:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] i dođeš,

444
00:24:20,740 --> 00:24:22,779
[SPEAKER_00] odjednom se nađeš u samostanu.

445
00:24:22,779 --> 00:24:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

446
00:24:24,019 --> 00:24:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] stavu ti daje upravo to dokazivanje Bogu.

447
00:24:27,319 --> 00:24:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dokazivanje da možeš ti to.

448
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da on može učiniti

449
00:24:33,420 --> 00:24:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] od tebe ribara ljudi.

450
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] Da on može učiniti od tebe

451
00:24:37,779 --> 00:24:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevca.

452
00:24:39,539 --> 00:24:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da on može učiniti od tebe

453
00:24:41,940 --> 00:24:44,640
[SPEAKER_00] ono za što si pozvan.

454
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je bitna reč, učiniti.

455
00:24:47,279 --> 00:24:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije isto vjerovati u Isusa,

456
00:24:51,359 --> 00:24:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] vjerovati u Boga

457
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] ili vjerovati Bogu Isusu.

458
00:24:54,740 --> 00:24:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] Sad gradimo neko drugo povjerenje.

459
00:24:58,220 --> 00:25:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] Gradimo to povjerenje oči u oči sa Bogom.

460
00:25:01,799 --> 00:25:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] On je kako vjerovati u Boga neka razina znanja,

461
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:07,319
[SPEAKER_01] dok jovo vam uvjerovati Bogu odnos.

462
00:25:07,319 --> 00:25:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] Odnos, sam odnos, oči u oči.

463
00:25:09,539 --> 00:25:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ta i ta jedna komunikacija.

464
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ako uzmemo najjednostavniju definiciju morlitve,

465
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] kako vlazi?

466
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:17,660
[SPEAKER_00] Razgova s Bogom.

467
00:25:17,660 --> 00:25:20,720
[SPEAKER_00] A često puta je nama ljudima se,

468
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] nama ljudima se često puta

469
00:25:23,319 --> 00:25:25,319
[SPEAKER_00] samima su oči s Bogom

470
00:25:25,319 --> 00:25:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] nijako teško.

471
00:25:26,579 --> 00:25:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se onda svočavamo u stvari sa samim sobom.

472
00:25:28,980 --> 00:25:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] Sa svim onim odvratnim što je u nama.

473
00:25:33,059 --> 00:25:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je Frano prvi put napravio

474
00:25:36,619 --> 00:25:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad se obratio?

475
00:25:38,279 --> 00:25:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Oša je i zagrlija je ono najodvratnije

476
00:25:41,579 --> 00:25:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] što je u životu mislio da je mu je najodvratnije,

477
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] a to je gubavca.

478
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:50,319
[SPEAKER_00] Znači trebamo priglediti ono najodvratnije u nama.

479
00:25:50,319 --> 00:25:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] Onaj nudna, onaj talog, talog u nama prihvatiti

480
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] i taj talog prinijeti upravo Bogu

481
00:25:57,079 --> 00:25:59,319
[SPEAKER_00] da on od toga taloga napravi

482
00:25:59,319 --> 00:26:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] upravo svećenika

483
00:26:02,319 --> 00:26:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] ili dobroga novinara

484
00:26:04,099 --> 00:26:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] ili dobre ljude,

485
00:26:06,359 --> 00:26:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] dobroga čovjeka u krajnom liniji.

486
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da on napravi tu,

487
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali treba se početi,

488
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] treba skupiti hrabrosti

489
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:16,200
[SPEAKER_00] i početi se dokazivati Bogu.

490
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] I ta godina postulatura je prošla u tome upravo.

491
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] U tome spoznavanju dokazivanja Bogu.

492
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] dolazimo na Visovac.

493
00:26:26,599 --> 00:26:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je ni mali otočić na krki.

494
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] Mali otočić na krki.

495
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] Novci i jad.

496
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] I zamis sad mene.

497
00:26:34,539 --> 00:26:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] Koji sve ovo prošao u životu.

498
00:26:38,059 --> 00:26:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] A ti nisču, ja savoden 10%.

499
00:26:41,059 --> 00:26:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] Koji sve prošao u životu.

500
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] Sad jedno zatvoreno.

501
00:26:45,059 --> 00:26:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila velika promjena.

502
00:26:48,799 --> 00:26:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo jako teško.

503
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jako teško mi je to bilo.

504
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] opet uz molitvu.

505
00:26:57,279 --> 00:27:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] Boga nikad ne isključujemo iz našeg života.

506
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:02,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet jedan ljudski faktor.

507
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sa mnom su tu bila tri sjemeništarca.

508
00:27:05,579 --> 00:27:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] I sinje.

509
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] Koja su već živjeli u tome života.

510
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:16,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da, on su od sjemeništa već četiri godine bil, pet godina u samostanu.

511
00:27:16,019 --> 00:27:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] I kad su mi došli u Novcijat, oni su meni tu pomogli jako.

512
00:27:21,599 --> 00:27:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

513
00:27:21,859 --> 00:27:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se ja u njima vidio da to nije baš ta samoća, da nije baš i taj život u samostanu, da nije to baš nešto ono što bi mene odbilo.

514
00:27:31,420 --> 00:27:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi mene odbilo.

515
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] I u tome, upravo na Visovcu, u Novcijatu, ulaziš dublje u život Svetoga Frane, ulaziš dublje u provinciju i ulaziš dublje u Isosov život.

516
00:27:48,279 --> 00:27:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] Tu se upravo stvaruje ono, dođi i vidi.

517
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kaže Isus, dođi i vidi.

518
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kaže, dođi gdje stanujem, dođi i vidi.

519
00:27:58,240 --> 00:28:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ipak od se svidi, ostani.

520
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] A ako se ne svidi, dođi drug gdje i vidi.

521
00:28:02,859 --> 00:28:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] I jednostavno, to je jedna ispunjenost i to je jedno prožimanje ljudi koji su bili sa mnom u Novcijatu.

522
00:28:10,859 --> 00:28:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] I pogotovo ta tri sjemeništarca, pogotovo njih,

523
00:28:18,279 --> 00:28:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] je mene udržalo na tome.

524
00:28:20,980 --> 00:28:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je meni jako teško razdoblje života bilo.

525
00:28:23,220 --> 00:28:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] Baš šta je ovoga.

526
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] To se ja uvijek nešto radi.

527
00:28:26,559 --> 00:28:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad nema odjedno ni društvenih mreža,

528
00:28:28,980 --> 00:28:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] nema odjedno ni bloga, nema ništa.

529
00:28:32,039 --> 00:28:34,700
[SPEAKER_01] Da, čovjek sad više nema gdje pobeći, ostaje sam sa sebo.

530
00:28:34,700 --> 00:28:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ostaješ sam sa sebo.

531
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je taj Novcijati dobar.

532
00:28:38,559 --> 00:28:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je taj Novcijati dobar jer ostaješ sam sa svojim Bogom,

533
00:28:42,460 --> 00:28:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] ostaješ sam sa seboj.

534
00:28:43,619 --> 00:28:47,359
[SPEAKER_00] Zuočavaš se s onim najgorijim unutar sebe.

535
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] unutar sebe.

536
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi studiranje u Splitu,

537
00:28:51,619 --> 00:28:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] šest godina fakulteta.

538
00:28:54,940 --> 00:29:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi jedno prodobljivanje vjere u Boga

539
00:29:01,059 --> 00:29:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] kroz fakultet i učenje.

540
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kreće, znači, pastoralna djelatnost.

541
00:29:08,779 --> 00:29:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje sam džakom bija u Gospe ozdravlja,

542
00:29:12,559 --> 00:29:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam i tebe upoznao.

543
00:29:14,099 --> 00:29:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] Zakom bija u Gospe ozdravlja u Splitu.

544
00:29:17,819 --> 00:29:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Prva služba mi je Gospa Vanka Grada u Šibeniku.

545
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je opet bila Gospa ozdravlja u Splitu.

546
00:29:27,759 --> 00:29:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] i sada Sveti Frano i Mocki.

547
00:29:30,519 --> 00:29:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gdje se časti Gospa od Anđela.

548
00:29:33,500 --> 00:29:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako ti ja volim reći onaj samo ove gradske Gospi.

549
00:29:36,980 --> 00:29:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ove gradske Gospi u Bilazin.

550
00:29:40,839 --> 00:29:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je, što je povuka ovoga?

551
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] Povuka je ovoga da mi možemo graditi ovozemalsko

552
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] ili sa ljudima možemo graditi zajedništvo,

553
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] možemo graditi povjerenje,

554
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako se mi sami ne suočimo s Bogom,

555
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] mi nemamo šta dati drugome.

556
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] Naprimjer, ja da tebe sad pitan daj mi čokoladu.

557
00:30:03,259 --> 00:30:05,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ti je nemaš, ti je moraš otići kupiti

558
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] ili je doniti iz druge prostorije.

559
00:30:06,799 --> 00:30:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako ti nešto nemaš u sebi,

560
00:30:09,339 --> 00:30:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] ako nemaš to jedno suočavanje sa sobom,

561
00:30:12,759 --> 00:30:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti nisi čist pred Bogom i pred ljudima,

562
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne moraš ti drugome doći i prihvatiti kao tako.

563
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:22,319
[SPEAKER_00] Drugu osobu ne moraš prihvatiti.

564
00:30:22,319 --> 00:30:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono možda što fali ovim mlađim generacijama,

565
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] što ja često naglašavam.

566
00:30:28,279 --> 00:30:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] Taj odnos oči u oči s Bogom.

567
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Oči u oči sa sebom.

568
00:30:32,539 --> 00:30:35,740
[SPEAKER_00] Biti strpljiv sa samim sobom.

569
00:30:35,740 --> 00:30:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] E kad tu postignemo razinu,

570
00:30:38,779 --> 00:30:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad se dokazujemo Bogu,

571
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] kad se dokazujemo onomu koji nas je stvorio,

572
00:30:44,559 --> 00:30:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] kad imamo povjerenja u Boga

573
00:30:46,519 --> 00:30:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] da može u našem životu učiniti čuda,

574
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] onda će nam život biti drugačiji.

575
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, na primjer, u Šibeniku

576
00:30:54,539 --> 00:30:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam jako teško od korone u bolnci.

577
00:30:58,279 --> 00:31:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo ti je sada svjedočanstvo,

578
00:31:01,319 --> 00:31:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, svjedočanstvo doktora

579
00:31:03,779 --> 00:31:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bija tu, kojim je pratio.

580
00:31:06,119 --> 00:31:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, mi smo učinili sve,

581
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam šta je tebe spaslo.

582
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govori, zna ja.

583
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] Digla se je tada

584
00:31:13,019 --> 00:31:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Dominik Ilić,

585
00:31:15,519 --> 00:31:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] Dominikanac,

586
00:31:16,460 --> 00:31:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] je objavio,

587
00:31:18,019 --> 00:31:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] tada se je digla,

588
00:31:18,799 --> 00:31:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] digle su se ove katolička vojska,

589
00:31:22,079 --> 00:31:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] se je digla u moltvu,

590
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] i meni je spasla moltvu.

591
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da, svako je na moltvu.

592
00:31:26,839 --> 00:31:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] Uz doktora.

593
00:31:27,859 --> 00:31:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] A da nije bilo doktora.

594
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] A da se je samo molu.

595
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,119
[UNKNOWN] Pitanje.

596
00:31:33,119 --> 00:31:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako često puta ja znam reći

597
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] mojim krizmanicima i framašima,

598
00:31:40,559 --> 00:31:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] ako sutra imaš ispit,

599
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] može ti izmoli pompejsku krunicu,

600
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti nešto položi tako ne naučiš.

601
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

602
00:31:47,059 --> 00:31:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi moramo dati nešto od sebe,

603
00:31:49,859 --> 00:31:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] je li, Bogu.

604
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:53,660
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo krenuti za Bogom

605
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] i pustiti njemu da nas On učini,

606
00:31:56,559 --> 00:31:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] učini njegovim svjedocima.

607
00:31:59,099 --> 00:32:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su mi to dobili,

608
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] svi su mi to dobili na krštenju.

609
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] Prorok, kralj, svećenik, svi.

610
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan od nas.

611
00:32:07,079 --> 00:32:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan od nas

612
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] je to dobijeno na krštenju.

613
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:13,839
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači proroku u današnje vrijeme, svjedok?

614
00:32:13,839 --> 00:32:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači kralju u današnje vrijeme?

615
00:32:16,819 --> 00:32:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] Biti ono što jesi.

616
00:32:18,279 --> 00:32:21,140
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo, kraljevati nad sebom,

617
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom,

618
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] i kraljevati nad drugima.

619
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:26,799
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači biti svećenik?

620
00:32:26,799 --> 00:32:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] Da smo svi sveti, u startu.

621
00:32:29,779 --> 00:32:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] Svi smo sveti.

622
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, biti svećenik

623
00:32:34,299 --> 00:32:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] u svome životu

624
00:32:36,079 --> 00:32:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] i svojim životom,

625
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] u svome staležu,

626
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,259
[SPEAKER_00] u svome pozivu,

627
00:32:40,259 --> 00:32:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] prinositi Bogu sebe,

628
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] prinositi Bogu druge,

629
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] prinositi Bogu cijeli svijet.

630
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] Samo što smo mi,

631
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] ministrijalno svećenstvo,

632
00:32:51,079 --> 00:32:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] a ministar ministrare znači

633
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] poslužitelj,

634
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] onaj koji služi.

635
00:32:55,259 --> 00:32:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je Isus na posljedno večer radio?

636
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nema tu ništa.

637
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] On je ustanovio sveti red,

638
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] je ustanovio Eucharistiju,

639
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] a šta je radio?

640
00:33:04,019 --> 00:33:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] O pravo noge,

641
00:33:06,140 --> 00:33:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] ljubio noge.

642
00:33:07,559 --> 00:33:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je važno.

643
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] Važno je i služiti.

644
00:33:12,359 --> 00:33:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] To smo mi ministrijalno svećenstvo.

645
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svi smo mi i proroci,

646
00:33:16,839 --> 00:33:17,640
[SPEAKER_00] i kraljevi,

647
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] i svećenici.

648
00:33:18,779 --> 00:33:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] Svi.

649
00:33:19,500 --> 00:33:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da nije crkve,

650
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi imali

651
00:33:25,279 --> 00:33:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] sakramente kao sresta spasenja.

652
00:33:28,599 --> 00:33:30,700
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaj, crkva nigdi ne govori

653
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] da se neko van crkve ne može spasti.

654
00:33:33,079 --> 00:33:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali govori da je potpuna istina u crkvi

655
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] i da je Krist prisutan u katoličkoj crkvi.

656
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] Prisutan je u svojoj riječi,

657
00:33:40,279 --> 00:33:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] prisutan je uloz svećenika

658
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] kada dijeli sakramente,

659
00:33:43,559 --> 00:33:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] prisutan je u prilikama kruha i vina,

660
00:33:45,900 --> 00:33:48,660
[SPEAKER_00] prisutan je prisutan je u narodu Božje,

661
00:33:48,660 --> 00:33:50,839
[SPEAKER_00] što učinstavu me najmanje,

662
00:33:50,839 --> 00:33:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] od mojih najmanje,

663
00:33:52,079 --> 00:33:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] od mojih braća meni učinstavu.

664
00:33:55,319 --> 00:33:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] Prisutan je i postoje sredstva spasenja,

665
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] a to si sveći sakramenat.

666
00:33:59,859 --> 00:34:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] I to je onda pustiti Bogu da radi,

667
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] da radi na nama.

668
00:34:05,019 --> 00:34:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne možeš ti započeći radi kuću,

669
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] a ne kupiti ciglu,

670
00:34:11,079 --> 00:34:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne kupiti beto,

671
00:34:12,019 --> 00:34:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] ne kupiti ne znam šta.

672
00:34:14,179 --> 00:34:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš počeći radi kuću,

673
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] neće se ona sama od sebe graditi.

674
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:20,280
[SPEAKER_00] Znači opet moramo proći tu jedno

675
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] našo životno strpljenje

676
00:34:23,159 --> 00:34:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] prema samima sebi

677
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] i krenuti se dokazivati Bogu.

678
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako se ne dokazujemo Bogu,

679
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:32,840
[SPEAKER_00] nećemo dobro proći, nećemo.

680
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] Često spominješ to dokazivanje,

681
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] dokazivanje ljudima,

682
00:34:36,179 --> 00:34:37,599
[SPEAKER_01] što stoji je iza toga?

683
00:34:37,599 --> 00:34:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to možda neka nedovoljna svjesnost

684
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] svog lastog identiteta?

685
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Stojite ovo.

686
00:34:43,539 --> 00:34:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] Što će drugi pjeskati?

687
00:34:46,619 --> 00:34:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] Što će drugi dati tišću lajkova

688
00:34:49,199 --> 00:34:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] na društvenim mrežama?

689
00:34:50,199 --> 00:34:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Eko, ja.

690
00:34:53,519 --> 00:34:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi ćemo uvijek naći sebi

691
00:34:55,659 --> 00:34:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] slične,

692
00:34:57,079 --> 00:34:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] sebi slične,

693
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji će nas hvaliti.

694
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] I to onda postaje kriza identiteta,

695
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] što se rekao.

696
00:35:05,159 --> 00:35:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ta ego prelazi u krizu identiteta,

697
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] u sebe ljubi.

698
00:35:09,019 --> 00:35:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] U sebe ljubi.

699
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nema više ni zajednice,

700
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] nema više ni određenih ljudi

701
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji se okuplja oko jedne ideje.

702
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] nema više u krajinoj linii ni te ideje.

703
00:35:19,019 --> 00:35:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] Samo sam ja.

704
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] I meni pljesku.

705
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] I meni pljesak ide.

706
00:35:24,239 --> 00:35:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je super.

707
00:35:25,539 --> 00:35:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] E,

708
00:35:27,139 --> 00:35:29,739
[SPEAKER_00] i to godi, godi, godi.

709
00:35:29,739 --> 00:35:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to prođe.

710
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] To prođe,

711
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] najmanje rasprši se

712
00:35:34,539 --> 00:35:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] ko baluno sa punice.

713
00:35:36,139 --> 00:35:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] Rasprši se u sekundijan.

714
00:35:40,119 --> 00:35:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

715
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je to prolazna slava.

716
00:35:43,460 --> 00:35:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je

717
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] upravo to dokazivanje,

718
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] da je to negdje tu.

719
00:35:50,199 --> 00:35:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kaže Isus

720
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:53,719
[SPEAKER_00] kada poziva

721
00:35:53,719 --> 00:35:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] na sve u službu,

722
00:35:56,079 --> 00:35:56,739
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

723
00:35:56,739 --> 00:35:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] budite na svijetu,

724
00:35:58,679 --> 00:35:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne od svijeta.

725
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da svijet upravo nudi

726
00:36:01,860 --> 00:36:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] i tu je taj ja negoizam,

727
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] taj jedno pljeskanje,

728
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] to jednu pohvalu,

729
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:08,219
[SPEAKER_00] tu jednu pohvalu

730
00:36:08,219 --> 00:36:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] koja prolazi,

731
00:36:09,179 --> 00:36:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja će sutra,

732
00:36:11,539 --> 00:36:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti izraziš

733
00:36:13,099 --> 00:36:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] svoj nekakav stav

734
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] prema nečemu,

735
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] prema bilo čemu,

736
00:36:17,119 --> 00:36:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] koja će ti donijeti

737
00:36:18,599 --> 00:36:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] druge ljude

738
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji će te hvaliti.

739
00:36:20,599 --> 00:36:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] A ovi ljudi

740
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] što ste hvalili dotad,

741
00:36:22,900 --> 00:36:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] oni će te kuditi.

742
00:36:24,159 --> 00:36:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kod Isusa nema toga.

743
00:36:25,619 --> 00:36:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nije umata u celofan

744
00:36:28,460 --> 00:36:29,199
[SPEAKER_00] da će nam biti

745
00:36:29,199 --> 00:36:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] lijepo,

746
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] lijepo

747
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] i da će umisak skaka,

748
00:36:32,079 --> 00:36:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] polivad i plesat.

749
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] To nije Isus rekao.

750
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je rekao,

751
00:36:35,739 --> 00:36:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] progonit će vas

752
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] zbog moga imena.

753
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:39,380
